I really love these movies.  They are classics that always make me laugh!  Parenthood is sweet and touching, with some hard to watch awkward moments--just like real life parenting!  Housesitter also stars Goldie Hawn as the last person Steve Martin expects to fall in love with!  Worth buying and adding to your movie library!
I love both these films.  I chose a four star instead of a five because the 2 movies were on one disc.  I would still recommend business with these folks.

Some of the old movies are not only the funniest but make great watching over and over.  I was very pleased when I noticed that these were two for one.  I got it in a heartbeat.  The main chapters have been leads in several other movies.  These are two funny people who make you laugh.  I found the service organization to be very helpful.  Over the holidays lost of mail gets lost or at least we don,t get them.  It is really fine having a back up organization which will help to the extreme.  Heck they even ask if I was happy with their service.  I can assure you I am and was.

Steve Martin is one of my favorite actors, and both of these movies have long been favorites as well.  Goldie Hawn shines in Housesitter, and the movie it so funny!  Parenthood is hilarious, and I can watch it over and over and just never tire of it.  These films are an absolute must for any Steve Martin fan!

The movie was shipped right away and actually made it to my mailbox right after that. In my experience, that does not happen very often. I only wanted one movie but it was sold as a double feature, two good movies for the price of one, can't beat that.
